      "value": "<p>This section covers the usage of Tractor's APIs and job scripting syntax.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table style=\"margin-left: 10.0px;\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><div class=\"first last line-block\"><div class=\"line\"><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/TRA/pages/22184254/Job+Scripting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22184254\" data-linked-resource-version=\"25\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Job Scripting</a></div></div></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">The Tcl-based syntax for authoring jobs.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><div class=\"first last line-block\"><div class=\"line\"><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/TRA/pages/22184314/Job+Author+Python+API\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22184314\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Job Author API</a></div></div></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">The Python API for authoring jobs.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><div class=\"first last line-block\"><div class=\"line\"><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/TRA/pages/22184266/Query+Python+API\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22184266\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Query API</a></div></div></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">The Python API for query and control of jobs, tasks, commands, and blades.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><div class=\"first last line-block\"><div class=\"line\"><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/TRA/pages/22184260/Tractor+URL+API\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22184260\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">URL API</a></div></div></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">The URL API for communicating directly with the engine.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><div class=\"first last line-block\"><div class=\"line\"><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/TRA/pages/22184262/Search+Clauses\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22184262\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Search Clause Syntax</a></div></div></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">The syntax used in the Dashboard, tq, and query API for searching for jobs, tasks, commands, and blades.</td></tr></tbody></table></div>"
